	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=classes.html?class=15&mid=10346987689316>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=15&mid=10346987689316>RE: which is better</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=15&mid=10346987689316#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Tue, Oct 15th 12:19 PM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=93357><span id=Scholar>PsychosisKaos</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>56 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [2.88]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Thats all depending on what you want. Compare the Races.<br><br>Vash Shir<br>Barbarian<br>Oger<br>Troll<br>Iskar<br><br>So lets take a look at each Races pros and cons<br>(This information is found also on the following Beaslord Sites<br><a href=HTTP://www.eqbeastlord.com target=_new>Eq Beastlord</a><br><a href=HTTP://patriot.net/~dios/bst target=_new>Katrinas Beastlord Guide</a><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>Barbarians<br><br>Traits:<br>- Good Aligned--Barbarians can travel in most cities unharmed<br>- Decently built for Melee and Casting, Good Str/Sta, Decent Wis.<br>- No large racial EXP penalty<br>- No Nightvision<br>- Save vs. Cold bonus<br><br><br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br><br>Iksars<br><br>Traits:<br>- KoS in al cities but Shar Vahl and Coldain(Thurgadin)<br>- Better Casting-oriented race, High Wis(for beastlords), but low str/sta<br>- ~20% racial EXP penalty<br>- Infravision<br>- Save vs. Fire Bonus<br>- Save vs. Cold Penalty<br>- Regen 2x Normal regen rate.<br>- Forage<br>- Cannot use Plate Armor<br>- Natura AC Bonus<br><br><br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br><br>Ogres<br><br>Traits:<br>- Evil, Allied with Dark Elves and Trolls<br>- Awsome melee stats, but the low wis hurts them for casting<br>- ~15% racial EXP penalty<br>- Infravision<br>- Cannot be stunned by melee attacks from the front<br><br><br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br><br>Trolls<br><br>Traits:<br>- Evil, Allied with Dark Elves and Trolls<br>- High Stamina, Good Str, Low wis, great melee race.<br>- ~20% racial EXP penalty<br>- Infravision<br>- Save vs. Fire Penalty<br>- Regen 2x Normal regen rate.<br><br><br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br><br>Vah Shir<br><br>Traits:<br>- KoS to Iksars, trolls, ogres, and most likely dark elves too<br>- The 'balanced' race, str/sta/wis all average<br>- Small racial EXP penalty<br>- Infravision<br>- Innate Safe Fall (50)<br>- Innate Sneak (50)<br>- Consumes food 2x faster<br></p>&nbsp;<br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=408169 target=_new>Soriab Whitebeast 64 Savage Lord</a><br>Firestormers</td></td></tr>
